SearchPropertyComparator
public class RegExpPropertyComparator
extends PropertyComparator

A Filter using regular expressions. For optimum speed the pattern is precompiled. IMPORTANT: As SQL does not know RegExps, the Expression-Representation of this Filter is: ' ilike '

Ridcully
